      "$component": true,
      "$content": true,
      "$definition": true,
      "_id": "page.future-resources---content--3",
      "_type": "content",
      "html": "## Find a legal service provider ##\r\n\r\n### Find a solicitor ###\r\n[Find a Solicitor](https://solicitors.lawsociety.org.uk) is a free service for anyone looking for information about organisations or people providing legal services in England and Wales that are regulated by the Solicitors Regulation Authority (SRA). \r\n\r\n### Law Works ###\r\nThe LawWorks Clinics Network provides free initial advice to individuals on housing matters. Find out more at [https://www.lawworks.org.uk/](https://www.lawworks.org.uk/).\r\n\r\n### Law Centre Network ###\r\nLaw Centres offer legal advice, casework and representation to individuals and groups. The Law Centre Network helps users to locate a law centre. Find out more at [www.lawcentres.org.uk](https://www.lawcentres.org.uk)\r\n\r\n### Legal Choices ###\r\nLegal Choices gives you independent, factual information about legal issues and legal advisers. Read their [guide to housing and legal issues] (https://www.legalchoices.org.uk/legal-choices/got-a-legal-issue/houses).  \r\n\r\n### Advocate ###\r\nAdvocate is a charity that offers free legal assistance from volunteer barristers. [https://weareadvocate.org.uk/](https://weareadvocate.org.uk/).",
